## Installation
### Using pip/pipx
Use the following command to install the CLI application -

```zsh
pip install tizori-cli
```
or
```zsh
pipx install tizori-cli
```

<br>
<br>


## Usage

Use the following command for help -
```zsh
tizori --help
```

<br>
